name: The Love's Maiden Voyage Collection
description:
The Love's Maiden Voyage Collection 
*1912
*Dinner at 8 o'clock 
*Jack's Rose
*The Heart Of The Ocean

name: The Heart Of The Ocean
description: From the Love's Maiden Voyage Collection, inspired by The Titanic, The Heart Of the Ocean is a vibrant jelly navy blue scattered holographic

From the Love's Maiden Voyage Collection, inspired by The Titaninc, 1912 is a thermal medium gray shade loaded with small square holographic glitter. It changes from medium to light gray depending on the temperature.

name: Dinner at 8
description:
From the Love's Maiden Voyage collection, inspired by The titanic, this is Dinner at 8 o'clock. 
A clear base packed with large round silver holographic glitter, small brown glitter and bronze glitter. The picture shows two coats over OPI Don't Pretzel My Buttons.

name: Jack's Rose
description: From the Love's Maiden Voyage Collection, inspired by The Titanic, Jack's Rose is a delicate nude off white crelly base loaded with a rose gold micro flakes and a subtle violet shimmer in it.

name: Black Tie
description:
Black Tie is a clear base packed with micro holographic black glitter, square silver holo, silver dots and black bows glitter. 

The picture shows Black Tie over OPI Skull and Glossbones.

name: Cocktail Dress
description:
Cocktail Dress is a white crelly base with magenta dots and squares, pink dots, square purple holo glitter, hex matte light pink and pink bows. 
The picture shows three thin coats by itself.

name: Sweet Diamonds
description:
This is a Limited Edition shade.
Sweet Diamonds is a clear base with micro holographic glitter in different colors. 
It's opaque in three thin coats.

name: Magical
description: Magical is a clear base with black and white iridescent glitter in various shapes and sizes, black and white matte glitter and white mate shredded glitter.

name: Rudolph's Nose
description: A medium red scattered holo.

name: Cherry Pie
description: Holographic deep cherry red.

name: Arbolito
description:
Arbolito is a scattered holo crelly green .

Thank you very much to Sarah from Lethallacquer.blogspot.com for the swatches.

name: Don't Open 'till Christmas
description: This is a clear base packed with different size of glitters in various colors. This can be layered over any shade.

name: Hot Cocoa
description: Medium shimmery brown scattered holo.

name: Golden Kisses
description: Shimmery gold with a subtle scattered holo.

name: Santa's Workshop
description:
White crelly base with gold shimmer and red, green, and gold glitter in different sizes and various shapes. 


Thank you very much to Sarah from Lethallacquer.blogspot.com for the swatches.

name: Snow Globe
description:
White shimmery base with micro blue holo glitter. 

Thank you very much to Sarah from Lethallacquer.blogspot.com for the swatches.

name: Fall Is In The Air
description:
Shimmery brown scattered holo.


Thank you very much to Sarah from Lethallacquer.blogspot.com for the swatches.

name: Autumn Memories
description: Creme mustard yellow scattered holo.

name: Blueberry Mango Sorbet
description: Orange pastel base with small periwinkle glitter, square orange and iridescent bar glitter.

name: Blizzard
description: White Shimmery Crelly (creme/jelly) base with gold and silver glitter.

name: Lovely Pink
description: This is a white jelly base with purple, red, pink and white glitter in different shapes and sizes, iridescent micro glitter and light pink stars.

name: Cupcake Fantasy
description: This is a mixture of various colored glitter in different shapes and sizes in a jelly/creme light pink-lavender base.

name: Pop Tart
description:
White jelly base with matte glitters in yellow, orange, green, gray and watermelon in different shapes and sizes.
This is two coats over white.

name: Shark Attack
description:
Shark Attack is a jelly periwinkle shade full of square and hexagonal magenta glitters and small round blue glitter.
I used three thin coats for the swatch below.

name: Sweet Tooth
description:
Sweet Tooth is a clear base packed with neon glitter in different shapes and sizes including neon pink stars. 
I used two coats over black and white for the picture below.

name: Concrete Glamour
description:
This is a white jelly base with pastel blue and pink glitters, small squares in purple and matte gray dots.
This is two coats over white.

name: Hero In Disguise
description: Hero in Disguise is a jelly matte gray shade with a subtle blue shimmer with red and yellow matte glitter and black stars.

name: I Smell Spring
description:
This is a yellowish nude jelly base with multicolored glitter in different sizes and shapes. 
This is a 3 free polish.
Size:15ml

name: Inner Princess
description: White base with navy blue flakes, mix of multicolored glitter and aqua stars shape glitter.

name: BPFF (Best Polish Friend Forever)
description:
A slightly shimmery sky blue jelly base with small white hex glitter, large purple squares, small blue squares, teal and dark blue hex glitter and pink round glitter.
This is a 3 free polish.
Size:15ml

name: Holo Blast
description: Holo Blast is a holographic top coat that can be applied  over any shade to give it a stunning holographic effect.

name: Scary Layers
description: Clear base packed with glitters (orange, silver, green, black, red) and big black dots.  This can be layered over any shade.

name: Fancy Cauldron
description: Shimmery gold base with black, whiter and orange glitter in various shapes and sizes, opaque in three thin coats.

name: This is Halloween!
description: This is a white crelly base with peach shimmer, micro purple bars, small size square orange glitter, medium size purple glitter and medium black dots.

name: Sexy Bones
description: White crelly base with micro gold flakes, black bar glitter, silver, bronze and copper glitter.

name: Haunted Bubbles
description: White shimmery crelly (creme/jelly) base with round holo glitter in teal, green and silver, small navy blue square glitter and holo magenta glitter in hex shape.

name: Spooky Lights
description: Spooky Lights is a black jelly base full of  multicolored glitter in different shapes and sizes. This can be opaque with three thin coats or just layered over a black nail polish.

name: Ocean Breeze
description: Ocean Breeze is a medium shimmery blue base with teal dots, coral, green and blue glitters.

name: Fun In The Sun
description: This is a clear shimmery base packed with matte pastel glitters in different sizes and shapes.

name: Watermelon Explosion
description: Bright fuchsia/pink base with holographic micro glitter and small rectangular  black glitter.

name: Atomic Tangerine
description: This medium orange base is packed with purple micro bars, hot pink and green hexagonal shape glitter and black diamonds.

name: Hidden Glow Collection
description:
This collection includes eight crelly (creme/jelly) shades with micro black holographic glitter. 
These shades  glow in the dark  after being exposed to light. This effect lasts a couple of minutes until you expose your nails to light again.
